      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " لَا تُكَرِّهُوا إِلَى أَنْفُسِكُمُ الْعِبَادَةَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father and Muhammad Bin Ismail, from al Fazl Bin Shazaan altogether, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hafs Bin Al Bakhtary, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Do not make the worship to be abhorrent to yourselves’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father and Muhammad ibn Isma’il from Fadl ibn Shadhan all from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hafs ibn al-Bakhtari from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) has said, ‘Do not cause your souls to dislike worship.’” "
        ]
      }
